{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 When plaintiff initiated the litigation, she and all four defendants were directors of the Conrad Prebys Foundation (the Foundation), a nonprofit public benefit corporation named for its founder.
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
